text: The Counter-Strike 1.6 Leet Crew terrorist faction was proto-Chudjakian
Honestly if I know my wife is not going to get a heart attack over it, I'm definitely going for a Jerahmeel/Joshbekashah type name for like a fifth son

Blackpilled at my grandfather donating the family ceremonial military sword to a history museum before I was born, but the LARPing potential having access to it would have unlocked would have distracted me from my Faucian studies

Found out that Dr. Harold Hillman (guy who was against electron microscopy, disproved a lot of cell organelles as image/histology stain artifacts) had a father who worked as "producer of stained glass", something very subtle connecting them, lenses, glasses, color, stains, light.

The same principle guiding design of church windows, stained glass on cathedrals, "rose windows", etc. also apply to microscopy work and illuminating cells. It's very funny, but I see figures like Dr. Hillman or Dr. Gilbert Ling as being the microcosm equivalent of flat earthers.

Also he's apparently Jewish. Last night I also found out the biorhythms marine biologist professor guy whose articles I was reading was black. No idea what's going on. I'm expecting a Blasian researcher next.
It's pretty amusing how the "worker standing up to speak" image is literal FDR war propaganda, essentially waving the UN battle flag (four stripes for FDR's four freedoms)
The joker as a playing card is such a funny concept, a literal "now let's do a silly one"
I have appreciated every single thing you have said to me here. Thank you, I truly appreciate it and am glad I made you smile sometimes. God bless you and may He protect you in all your days.
